trans-unit.source: Enumeration of activity result values that qualifies the state of an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that has an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Closed" name="Closed" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Enumeração de valores de resultado de atividade que qualificam o estado de um <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> que tenha um <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> de <xref uid="langword_csharp_Closed" name="Closed" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Result represents the final status of an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> instance within a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Resultado representa o estado final de um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>instância dentro de uma instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: The values of the enumeration are based upon the activity state diagram that is determined by the activity-engine contract.
trans-unit.target: Os valores de enumeração baseiam-se o diagrama de estado de atividade que é determinado pelo contrato do motor de atividade.

trans-unit.source: Values other than None are allowed only for an activity whose <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> is <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>.
trans-unit.target: Os valores que não sejam None só são permitidos para uma atividade cujo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>é <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the canceling state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade transitou para o estado fechado do Estado de cancelamento.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the compensating state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade transitou para o estado fechado do Estado compensating.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the faulting state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade transitou para o estado fechado do Estado faulting.

trans-unit.source: The activity is not in the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus.Closed> state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade não está a ser o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus.Closed>Estado.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus.Closed>

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the executing state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade transitou para o estado fechado do Estado de execução.

trans-unit.source: The activity has transitioned to the closed state from the initialized state.
trans-unit.target: A atividade transitou para o estado fechado do Estado inicializado.
